  "code": "%%{init: {\"quadrantChart\": {\"quadrantPadding\": 10}, \"theme\": \"forest\", \"themeVariables\": {\"quadrant1TextFill\": \"blue\"}} }%%\nquadrantChart\n  x-axis Urgent --> Not Urgent\n  y-axis Not Important --> important\n  quadrant-1 Plan\n  quadrant-2 Do\n  quadrant-3 Delegate\n  quadrant-4 Delete",
