  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想做一个四象限图表，用来展示任务优先级矩阵。横轴是紧急程度，从Urgent到Not Urgent，纵轴是重要性，从Not Important到Important。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "x-axis",
        "y-axis",
        "quadrantChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，就是艾森豪威尔矩阵对吧？那四个象限的标签您打算怎么命名？第一象限是紧急且重要的，通常叫Do？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "quadrant-1",
        "quadrant-2",
        "quadrant-3",
        "quadrant-4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第一象限Plan，第二象限Do，第三象限Delegate，第四象限Delete。等等，让我想想，第一象限应该是Do，紧急重要立即执行；第二象限才是Plan，重要但不紧急的需要计划。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "quadrant-1",
        "quadrant-2"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我调整一下：quadrant-1是Plan，quadrant-2是Do。那第三象限Delegate是紧急但不重要的任务委托给他人，第四象限Delete是不紧急也不重要的直接删除，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "quadrant-1",
        "quadrant-2",
        "quadrant-3",
        "quadrant-4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。另外我想用forest主题，并且把第一象限的文字颜色改成蓝色，这样Plan部分更突出。还有象限之间的间距设置成10。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "theme",
        "themeVariables",
        "quadrant1TextFill",
        "quadrantPadding"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已经配置好了，init参数里设置了forest主题、quadrantPadding为10，还有quadrant1TextFill为blue。您看看效果是否符合预期？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "init",
        "quadrantChart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "纵轴的标签我写的是Not Important -- important，这里important的首字母应该大写，和Not Important保持一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "y-axis",
        "important"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，y-axis现在是Not Important -- Important。整个四象限图完成了：横轴Urgent到Not Urgent，纵轴Not Important到Important，四个象限分别是Plan、Do、Delegate、Delete。",
